{"tid":1793530,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"浸大生跳樓亡　fb遺言：唔好信一地兩檢","createTime":"2019-12-22T12:49:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-24T06:08:33.000Z","uid":67089,"like":30,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"1fa09fcb4209d6fc506b8e1a3f9d2965791cdb0e","tid":1793530,"uid":67089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T12:49:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171216/20246426\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171216%2F20246426&d=QEbR3JiquQCbCEiBABctD5bpPLVkgxcsq72qYZiHPFQ%3D&h=6837fb4d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171216%2F20246426&h=a2c89eea\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171216/20246426</a><br />\n【本報訊】一名25歲浸會大學男生，昨晨在facebook留言「千奇（祈）唔好信一地兩檢無跨境執法，再見各位！」6分鐘後被發現從九龍塘浸大教學及行政大樓高處墮下，救護員到場將事主送院證實不治，警方調查發現他一年前涉及一宗與繼母互毆案，事後離家租住酒店獨居，近日警方正式將他和繼母同時拘捕。至於他的自殺原因，警方仍在調查中。"},{"pid":"45af5ba598407d7eba547720f98f699ea9d4b072","tid":1793530,"uid":311583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T12:50:51.000Z","msg":"【核彈】呢個方法可以防水炮車【行動po求推】<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1778898\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1778898</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【置頂】【行動po求推】好㷫呀！警曱向人群舉槍，聽日同我即刻行動。而嚟緊嘅行動係1223stuck稅局<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1793389\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1793389</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CgxvfDH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCgxvfDH.jpg&h=8ac82a2a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jZLHRcb.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjZLHRcb.gif&h=42707f7c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jZLHRcb.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi